<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:53:39 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>游说团体警告欧洲企业对中国不利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/european-firms-souring-china-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-10/</link><description>欧洲商业游说团体周五表示，将中国列为顶级投资目的地的欧洲企业比例创下历史新低，并警告称，可能需要数年时间才能恢复人们对世界第二大经济体的信心。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:35:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/european-firms-souring-china-lobby-group-warns-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>油价因中国数据走强和中东冲突而上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-up-stronger-chinese-data-middle-east-conflict-2024-05-10/</link><description>周五油价上涨，因中国经济改善的迹象以及以色列和哈马斯之间停止敌对行动的谈判没有取得成果，油价继续上涨。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:14:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-prices-up-stronger-chinese-data-middle-east-conflict-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>美国立法者公布法案，更容易限制人工智能模型的出口</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-unveil-bill-make-it-easier-restrict-exports-ai-models-2024-05-10/</link><description>周三晚间，两党立法者小组公布了一项法案，该法案将使拜登政府更容易对人工智能模型实施出口管制，以保护珍贵的美国技术免受外国不良行为者的侵害。</description><pubDate>Fri, 10 May 2024 00:06:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/us-lawmakers-unveil-bill-make-it-easier-restrict-exports-ai-models-2024-05-10/</guid></item><item><title>为什么中国对人民币贬值的容忍可能是暂时的</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/why-chinas-tolerance-cheaper-currency-may-be-temporary-2024-05-09/</link><description>货币市场正在解读中国当局发出的微妙信号，表明他们正在慢慢压低人民币汇率以恢复出口竞争力，但分析师表示，人民币长期贬值既不是有意的，也是不可取的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 23:03:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/why-chinas-tolerance-cheaper-currency-may-be-temporary-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国委员会针对佐治亚理工学院涉嫌与中国军事相关研究的联系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-committee-targets-georgia-techs-alleged-ties-chinese-military-linked-research-2024-05-09/</link><description>美国国会中国问题委员会已要求顶尖研究型大学佐治亚理工学院详细说明与一所中国大学的合作细节，该大学因涉嫌与美国军方有联系而面临美国政府的限制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 20:55:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-committee-targets-georgia-techs-alleged-ties-chinese-military-linked-research-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，中国 Zeekr 将美国 IPO 定价定为区间上限，融资 4.41 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-ev-maker-zeekr-prices-us-ipo-top-range-raise-441-million-source-says-2024-05-09/</link><description>一位知情人士称，中国电动汽车制造商智客智能科技周四将其美国首次公开募股 (IPO) 定价定为指定区间的最高价，筹集了 4.41 亿美元。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 19:04:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-ev-maker-zeekr-prices-us-ipo-top-range-raise-441-million-source-says-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>路透调查显示中国4月份新增人民币贷款下降，政策支持到位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-new-yuan-loans-seen-falling-policy-support-place-2024-05-09/</link><description>路透调查显示，尽管央行继续保持对经济的政策支持，但由于季节性因素，中国四月份新增人民币贷款可能较三月份大幅下降。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 17:51:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-april-new-yuan-loans-seen-falling-policy-support-place-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>受中国市场打击，菲拉格慕第一季度收入下降 17%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-ferragamo-down-17-first-quarter-2024-05-09/</link><description>意大利奢侈品集团 Salvatore Ferragamo 第一季度的收入按固定汇率计算下降了 16.6%，原因是中国市场处境艰难，而且所有地区和渠道的销售普遍放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 16:09:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-ferragamo-down-17-first-quarter-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国企业因间谍气球事件受到美国贸易限制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-administration-adds-37-chinese-entities-trade-restriction-list-2024-05-09/</link><description>拜登政府周四将 37 个中国实体列入贸易限制名单，其中一些实体涉嫌支持去年飞越美国上空的间谍气球，加剧了北京和华盛顿之间的紧张关系。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:51:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/biden-administration-adds-37-chinese-entities-trade-restriction-list-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>解释者：先进的人工智能模型落入坏人之手会带来哪些风险？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-risks-do-advanced-ai-models-pose-wrong-hands-2024-05-09/</link><description>据路透社周三报道，拜登政府准备开辟一条新战线，努力保护美国人工智能免受中国和俄罗斯的侵害，初步计划在最先进的人工智能模型周围设置护栏。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:23:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/what-risks-do-advanced-ai-models-pose-wrong-hands-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>美国与中国讨论朝鲜问题并表达遣返担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-discusses-north-korea-with-china-airs-repatriation-concerns-2024-05-09/</link><description>美国国务院表示，负责朝鲜事务的美国高级官员周四在东京与中国官员讨论了该问题，并对中国强行遣返朝鲜人表示担忧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 15:02:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-discusses-north-korea-with-china-airs-repatriation-concerns-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>印度应亲华领导人要求完成从马尔代夫撤军</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-completes-troop-exit-maldives-pro-china-leaders-request-2024-05-09/</link><description>新德里官员周四表示，在总统穆罕默德·穆伊祖的要求下，印度已用平民取代了马尔代夫的约 80 名士兵，穆伊祖已将马尔代夫的关系转向中国。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 14:49:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-completes-troop-exit-maldives-pro-china-leaders-request-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>Coach母公司Tapestry因美国和中国需求不温不火而下调销售预期</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-05-09/</link><description>Coach 手袋制造商 Tapestry 周四下调了年度销售预期，并且未达到第三季度收入预期，这表明北美和中国对其手提包和配饰的需求疲软。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/coach-parent-tapestry-misses-quarterly-revenue-expectations-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>中国对美国人工智能技术的依赖程度如何？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-dependent-is-china-us-artificial-intelligence-technology-2024-05-09/</link><description>据路透社报道，拜登政府计划对美国开发的人工智能（AI）模型设置护栏，这些模型为 ChatGPT 等流行聊天机器人提供支持，以保护该技术免受中国和俄罗斯等国家的侵害。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:29:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/how-dependent-is-china-us-artificial-intelligence-technology-2024-05-09/</guid></item><item><title>高管表示，中国比亚迪将考虑于 2025 年在欧洲建立第二家工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-will-consider-second-european-plant-2025executive-says-2024-05-09/</link><description>中国汽车制造商比亚迪欧洲董事总经理迈克尔舒周四表示，该公司将考虑于 2025 年在欧洲建设第二家组装厂。</description><pubDate>Thu, 09 May 2024 10:04:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/byd-will-consider-second-european-plant-2025executive-says-2024-05-09/</guid></item></channel></rss>